{"tid":446590,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌，比銀龍伏左","createTime":"2017-10-24T12:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T05:05:22.000Z","uid":136553,"like":11,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ee03bd9036a560e7fb6cd901c8d377e7388b4ed9","tid":446590,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:18:14.000Z","msg":"頂<br />\n啱啱去銅鑼灣間銀龍食左個牛腩撈麵，46蚊<br />\n落單果陣，個侍應問：飲咩<br />\n咁佢既然咁講啦 我就以為包野飲<br />\n咁我就講左熱華田<br />\n結果埋單果陣，屌你點解56既<br />\n後來望翻先知原來唔包野飲<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n點解問我「飲咩」而唔係「加唔加野飲」？<br />\n根本誤導顧客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n莫名其妙食個牛腩撈麵都要56蚊，食翠華好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec6b834ac9b0cb3b95ecf2906489c6524667242","tid":446590,"uid":34174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:19:19.000Z","msg":"擺明係誤導你 吹佢唔漲"},{"pid":"8b208dab51b172305b8d185654c32fccfa00b0a8","tid":446590,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:32:33.000Z","msg":"可唔可以同消委會投訴<br />\n越諗越燥"},{"pid":"ca040dd1e97e55e9bc6c23a0ea3e22c32cf05415","tid":446590,"uid":1188,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:37:15.000Z","msg":"如果佢問你食咩菜，唔通包埋碟菜呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2adeac8e69453e50e0c8367e575d0134181bdd","tid":446590,"uid":706,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:38:54.000Z","msg":"佢係有不足<br />\n但你應該反省下點解自己咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b3766a1710c025c2f11b3111722f8df7fec02e","tid":446590,"uid":67289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"你自己on9姐柒碌"},{"pid":"4e4e1365e18a733adc2f51bf5c5830659e3a6d2a","tid":446590,"uid":66514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:55:45.000Z","msg":"佢唔加啲白汁比你咪算好彩囉"},{"pid":"7c08030b3ba4d31d937b4f8f2068e08e6b428609","tid":4